# ðŸ”— Problem Link
[Click here to read the problem](https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/problems/searching-in-an-array-where-adjacent-differ-by-at-most-k0456/1?page=1&category=CPP&sortBy=submissions)

// x is the element to be searched in arr[0..n-1]
// such that all elements differ by at-most k.

class Solution {
  public:
    int findStepKeyIndex(vector<int>& arr, int k, int x) {
        for(int i=0; i<arr.size(); i++){
            if(arr[i]==x){
                return i;
            }
        }
        return -1;
    }
};
